{"tid":1753932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家不要忘記年輕人","createTime":"2019-11-25T05:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T07:12:56.000Z","uid":61396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b10e33fa5de0b75310a67d5b840bba9d216e3b","tid":1753932,"uid":61396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"還有數以十萬計沒有機會投票<br />\n最勇敢的青少年<br />\n在poly 有300多年輕人被登記<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位勇敢的青少年<br />\n<br />\n我們還沒勝利<br />\n明天要繼續抗爭<br />\n為了自己，為了青年們"},{"pid":"0097d45bafb6b2d5296f5fe7417ab8858d0b7519","tid":1753932,"uid":148013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:07:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"730767ecdd21106b9969f3901a560324aade34ea","tid":1753932,"uid":61396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d2ef968a2094730d5a84d7a9e8f6fc538545110","tid":1753932,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4640f1b353a79b24d0268c65d8338b38172eb090","tid":1753932,"uid":61396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"多謝各位仍在理大的人<br />\n<br />\n大家不要忘記他們"}]}